oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要寫素質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我起碼有兩三年真係以為質素係錯嘅中文<br />\n素質先係正宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但件事講緊已經係十幾年前<br />\n蝗語一早就慢慢入左香港<br />\n下個十年分分鐘全民蝗語 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9131fdd981a814f4eaeb29ec2482af15cff3c7","tid":658922,"uid":159414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"438f713e8e93f103d9d4f61698b9ace05682b417","tid":658922,"uid":180156,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"小佛肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無大佛肉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"讀過小學都用唔出小佛啦<br />\n唔識字仲要打咁大篇嘢<br />\n露對波出嚟咪大把厹護駕囉<br />\n點解要衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33ddd962ab02d91f057ccc627cc1883e37b6f9a","tid":658922,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c7cfb5c1b9a0e8662dfb97dd6de9bba89198cae","tid":658922,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46004688c2384d74eee37cd4993b9a008390796b","tid":658922,"uid":182927,"like":312,"dislike":3,"score":309,"quote":{"pid":"8f178ca0b0edadf7e26fbd5e33029f5091829c62","tid":658922,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/191228_1f23e55e7ccd6aa30a7535a24cf3d2ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F191228_1f23e55e7ccd6aa30a7535a24cf3d2ae.jpg&h=a080e93d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔評論當中嘅論點，但入面啲用字的確有啲問題令我好困擾...<br />\n<br />\n而家全部學校都係教學生用「素質」？<br />\n<br />\n原因係漢語大詞典同辭海都係咁講？<br />\n因為通識教生活素質係啱？<br />\n因為「質素」僅為港澳地區用語而非正統中文用字？<br />\n<br />\n唔好再話咩追源溯始質素同素質都啱之類嘅廢話，<br />\n係大陸自己喺五六十年代改辭海嗰陣改走埋質素二字，<br />\n<br />\n亦唔好再話咩咪咁執著D用字，<br />\n我地心知肚明教育局成班仆街喺到做緊啲乜撚嘢，<br />\n希望呢個世代班學生哥自己有返啲批判思考，<br />\n唔係學校教咩都一定啱"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"唔好話質素，剩係講那同哪，小同少已經唔係個個識得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"墮同墜今時今日個個調轉用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n墜樓、墜後中場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n墮機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"重有墜胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8ed35b279548cfea178a8765c0465de8aca310","tid":658922,"uid":34584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9315b0aa7a25f643e1abfa05ed230bc46e36a657","tid":658922,"uid":66158,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"應該關通識事<br />\n6年前嘅中四通識已素質素質咁教 <br />\n不過洗唔到我腦 因為由細到大都講同睇文係質素"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:30:19.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前中學通識個教畜見我寫質素扣撚咗我分 叫我寫番素質<br />\n諗落通識呢科真係好撚鬼<br />\n借批判思考為名 其實就第二樣嘢"},{"pid":"141d3ee909d631e9de6